<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13294</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咔嚓！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13295</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>闪电朝罗西击了过来，罗西迅速躲开，闪电击中了邮箱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咻！”罗西深呼了一口气，“差一点就——”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26175</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咔嚓！又一道闪电击了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西再次躲开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你以为你的速度很快吗，火箭女孩儿？”气象员喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我倒想看看你能不能躲开这个！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>气象员把另一个气象球抛向空中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“气象球，激活！”他喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大风刮了起来，把罗西吹倒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天空中下起了大雨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咔嚓！轰隆！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>许多道闪电划过，罗西一跃而起躲开了闪电。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听着，气象员。”罗西喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你那愚蠢的雷雨无法阻挡我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许吧。”气象员得意地笑了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我有可以阻挡你的东西。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把另一个气象球抛向空中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“气象球，激活！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西感觉到天气的变化。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>随着一阵轰隆隆的声音，大风刮得更猛烈了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘啊，发生什么事了？’罗西心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后她转头看见一个巨大的龙卷风正在向西街席卷而来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”罗西大叫着被狂风卷起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在风里转来转去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有点头晕了！”她大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西听到了一个声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“救命！”一个女人大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！救我！”一个男人大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙卷风把一辆公交车，一辆出租车和罗西一起卷上了天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的乘客都很害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151614</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘不好了！’罗西心想。‘我必须救这些人！’</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151615</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西用尽全力在龙卷风里飞行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她用一只手抓住了出租车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃！”她大喊着飞向公交车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“抓到了！”她紧紧抓住了公交车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175540</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她双手都抓着车，飞出了龙卷风，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175541</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179281</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>想找一个安全的地方把车放下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179282</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙卷风平息了，警察来到了小巷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183825</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“气象员在这儿！”一名警察喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要暴风雪！”气象员大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>并把另一个气象球抛向空中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天气突然变冷了。天空飘起了雪花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>街道上也刮起了强风。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪越下越大，很快路面都被雪覆盖住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>警车在厚厚的积雪上滑行着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>车子从车道滑到了人行道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>气象员回到他的货车里并按下一个键。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>货车收起了普通车轮，换成了雪地履带式车轮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229884</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈！”气象员大笑着离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>